title: AED Game Character Voice - Orc Warlord
description: Join the brutal and bloody reign of The Orc Warlord, a violent force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. Dont let his ill temper fool you! He has quite the funny side, if you live long enough to see it!
longDescription:

AED Game Character Voice - Orc Warlord voice-over sound library provides you with more than 275+ immersive, game-ready voice-over sound files, vocalizations, custom, character specific dialogue lines, stock non-player character dialogue lines, and everything needed to create compelling cinematic scenes, characters, and outstanding game-play audio experiences.Â 


The Orc Warlord's voice profile is deep, gritty and dripping violence and warlike vigor!. He is perfect for Villains and antagonists, in-game non-player characters or any antagonist game characters with elements of evil and aggressive, angry tendencies. His voice is ready for your game as is, provided in clean audio format in case you want to further process with vocals effects.


Features:


-Vocal Profile: Deep, Gritty, Cockney Accent, Aggressive

- Perfect for NPC's in game and/or film based trailers.

-Featuring custom lines and NPC stock lines like: Kill them, I will destroy you, Attack. Perfect for MMO's, RPG's MOBA and RTS games.

-Featuring a variety of laughing, fighting, jumping and pain vocalizations to fully flesh out your next hero or villain in game!

-Works with any DAW or Game Engine

- Royalty Free and YouTube friendly

- Ready to rock, straight out of the box!
